data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Villa Heights! This all-brick end-unit townhouse, built in 2020, epitomizes modern elegance and convenience. Boasting 3 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a detached 2-car garage, it offers ample space for comfortable living.    The main living level floor plan is open, creating a seamless flow between the kitchen, dining, and living areas—great for entertaining or everyday living.The kitchen is a culinary haven with granite counters and sleek stainless-steel appliances, excellent for preparing gourmet meals. Conveniently located, you're just moments away from shopping, dining, major roads, interstates, military bases, parks, and ODU and NSU campuses. Plus, enjoy leisurely visits to the Virginia Zoo with ease.    After a busy day, unwind in the tranquil, low-maintenance backyard—a serene retreat for relaxation. Don't miss this opportunity to own a stylish, contemporary home in a vibrant community. Discover your slice of paradise in Villa Heights!
